{"tid":2000971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我想問五四關香港人撚事呢","createTime":"2020-05-04T08:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T11:11:26.000Z","uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d51c329b806e3dcdd8c5261a743944835d0e8606","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"當大陸講緊五四 講緊德先生 賽先生<br />\n激烈咁全盤否定傳統 打倒孔家店<br />\n<br />\n香港大學一路延續古文教育<br />\n真係有響應嘅老老豆豆少之有少<br />\n港英為左抵抗五四民族主義 加強左傳統教育<br />\n但咁反而令香港係佢保護下<br />\n唔使承受大6果套艱辛嘅文化探索 <br />\n最終好揀唔揀揀咗共產主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講本身殖民地西方文化洗禮<br />\n根本唔需要再講德先生 賽先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一百年前香港人 同支那<br />\n起點已經唔同  <br />\n除咗係為左慶祝共產黨成立 <br />\n真係諗唔到有咩原因要慶祝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07687c150b9fb5b21c7a799b7005fe3cbf37a3f","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"f5bcac54b32b51fe48dffe737bcf0e1ec06fcad3","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"46dd6e4d89e746d8916d6cb663ba48623d4c93c2","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"74d0ff04ee044ef244fa888616d499ef1ff8ac43","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f203eed6b1e4e58e65c89b27e64bb0799a9ef531","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:12:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a8bec19e04c1d750b3d309ea3d7a63dd9cf042ca","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"57949446fec559f8ccd8600e4533bee6b7de119f","tid":2000971,"uid":259102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s